author: Deepika Jayaram
title: Honey Rose was nervous to act with Mohanlal!
text:
Working with Mohanlal would be a dream come true for actors from the younger lot.
In a recent interview, Honey Rose said that she was nervous to share screen space with Mohanlal. However, for the down-to-earth actor that Mohanlal was, things got better for her on the sets, said Honey.
She added that while things went awry during the shoot in Doha, it was his steadfast attitude that lifted the spirits of others.
